description: Taking note of how some Mesa refits eschewed interior cargo space for carrying pods on the exterior hull, Testudo was quick to capitalize on the opportunity with the Elephant. It's not pretty or comfortable, but it mounts sixty standardized cargo pods, with some operators opting to add even more.
